// This strategy checks changes between the different sections of the Squeeze Momentum Indicator.
// Light-Green to Dark-Green change is compared to former Light-Green to Dark-Green change.
// If the squeeze value is smaller and at the same time the price is higher then we short.
// Light-Red to Dark-Red change is compared to former Light-Red to Dark-Red change.
// If the squeeze value is higher and at the same time the price is lower then we long.
//
// This specific strategy also includes Risk Management.
// 
// It was originally tested at BTCUSDT pair and 1h timeframe.
